# Lahman Baseball Database
#
# This directory contains the lahman.sqlite database (gitignored).
# Users build the database locally using the build script.
#
# Build command:
#   python scripts/build_lahman_db.py
#
# This downloads the Lahman Database CSV files and creates lahman.sqlite.
# Data spans 1871-present (depending on source availability).
#
# Source: SABR (Society for American Baseball Research)
#   https://sabr.org/lahman-database
#
# Original creator: Sean Lahman
#   https://www.seanlahman.com/baseball-archive/statistics/
#
# Note: lahman.sqlite is gitignored because it's ~66MB and can be
# rebuilt from source. The build script handles downloading automatically.
